title: [Wii] Super Smash Bros 64 WAD With Title
description:
Super Smash Bros. 64 WAD file for use with WAD Manager.

It took me forever to find this file so I thought I'd share the wealth. 

This is Version 3 and has the title screen.

Works perfectly so far as I've seen, I've played all of the stages, and used all of the characters without problems. 

I will be seeding even if it says there are no seeders.

Have Fun!!!
